---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
import appInterface from '../../assets/build-in-public-kingo.avif';

// SEO Configuration
const title = "Baixar Clipes e VODs da Twitch (MP4) - DownKingo";
const description = "Baixe clipes, VODs e transmissões da Twitch em alta qualidade. Salve streams completas, highlights e clipes de seus streamers favoritos.";
const keywords = "baixar clipe twitch, download twitch vod, baixar stream twitch, twitch clip downloader, salvar vod twitch mp4";

const canonical = "https://downkingo.com/pt/twitch-downloader/";
const og = {
    basic: {
        title: "Baixar Clipes e VODs da Twitch (MP4) - DownKingo",
        type: "website",
        image: "https://downkingo.com/og-image.png",
        url: canonical
    }
};
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} lang="pt-BR" canonical={canonical} opengraph={og} keywords={keywords}>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative min-h-[80vh] flex flex-col items-center justify-center pt-24 px-6 overflow-hidden">
        <!-- Background Elements -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-premium opacity-20 pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-purple-500/20 blur-[120px] rounded-full opacity-20 pointer-events-none mix-blend-screen animate-pulse duration-[5000ms]"></div>

        <div class="relative z-10 text-center max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-10">
             <!-- Eyebrow -->
             <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 border border-purple-500/20 rounded-full pl-2 pr-4 py-1 bg-purple-500/5 backdrop-blur-md hover:border-purple-500/40 transition-colors mx-auto">
                <Icon name="simple-icons:twitch" class="text-purple-500" width={16} />
                <span class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest text-purple-200 uppercase">Twitch VOD & Clip Downloader</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Main Title (H1 SEO Optimized) -->
            <h1 class="font-black text-5xl md:text-8xl tracking-tighter uppercase leading-[0.9] select-none text-white drop-shadow-2xl text-center mx-auto max-w-full">
                Baixar Clipes {' '}<br />{' '} <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-b from-purple-400 to-purple-800">da Twitch.</span>
            </h1>

            <p class="text-muted text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                Baixe clipes, VODs e transmissões completas da Twitch em alta qualidade. Salve highlights e streams dos seus streamers favoritos.
            </p>

            <!-- Actions -->
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-6 pt-8">
                 <a id="hero-download-btn" href="/pt/download/" class="h-14 px-10 bg-white text-black font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-gray-200 transition-all rounded-full flex items-center gap-3 hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(255,255,255,0.3)]">
                         <span id="hero-download-text">Baixar Grátis</span>
                         <Icon id="hero-download-icon" name="lucide:arrow-down" width={20} />
                 </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features Section SPECIFIC TO TWITCH -->
    <section id="features" class="py-24 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto border-y border-white/5 bg-black/20">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- Feature 1 -->
            <div class="p-8 border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] rounded-2xl hover:bg-white/[0.04] transition-colors group">
                <div class="mb-6 p-3 bg-purple-500/10 w-fit rounded-lg text-purple-500 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                    <Icon name="lucide:tv" width={32} />
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2 uppercase">VODs Completos</h2>
                <p class="text-xs text-muted leading-relaxed font-mono">
                    Baixe streams inteiras antes que sejam deletadas. Salve VODs completos de horas de transmissão em alta qualidade no seu dispositivo.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 2 -->
            <div class="p-8 border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] rounded-2xl hover:bg-white/[0.04] transition-colors group">
                <div class="mb-6 p-3 bg-purple-500/10 w-fit rounded-lg text-purple-500 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                    <Icon name="lucide:scissors" width={32} />
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2 uppercase">Clipes em HD</h2>
                <p class="text-xs text-muted leading-relaxed font-mono">
                    Salve highlights e clipes virais em qualidade máxima. Baixe os melhores momentos das streams em MP4 Full HD.
                </p>
            </div>

             <!-- Feature 3 -->
             <div class="p-8 border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] rounded-2xl hover:bg-white/[0.04] transition-colors group">
                <div class="mb-6 p-3 bg-purple-500/10 w-fit rounded-lg text-purple-500 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                    <Icon name="lucide:message-circle" width={32} />
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2 uppercase">Chat Replay</h2>
                <p class="text-xs text-muted leading-relaxed font-mono">
                    Opção de baixar com sobreposição de chat. Reviva a experiência completa da stream com as mensagens do chat integradas ao vídeo.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Visual Demo Section -->
    <section class="py-32 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
            <div class="space-y-8">
                <span class="inline-block mb-4 font-mono text-xs text-purple-500 uppercase tracking-widest border border-purple-500/20 bg-purple-500/5 px-2 py-1 rounded">Tecnologia yt-dlp</span>
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-white">Mais Rápido que {' '}<br />{' '} Qualquer Site.</h2>
                <p class="text-muted text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    Sites de download online são lentos, cheios de pop-ups e limitam a velocidade.
                    O DownKingo roda nativamente no seu Windows, Mac ou Linux, usando toda a sua banda para baixar VODs e clipes da Twitch instantaneamente.
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-4 pt-4">
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-300">
                        <Icon name="lucide:check" class="text-green-500" width={18} /> Sem limite de velocidade
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-300">
                        <Icon name="lucide:check" class="text-green-500" width={18} /> Sem anúncios ou pop-ups
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-300">
                        <Icon name="lucide:check" class="text-green-500" width={18} /> Sem compressão de qualidade
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Image Container -->
            <div class="relative group perspective-container">
                 <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600/20 to-purple-400/20 rounded-xl blur-xl opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700"></div>
                 <div class="relative rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-white/10 shadow-2xl bg-[#050505] rotate-3d hover:transition-transform duration-500">
                      <Image src={appInterface} format="webp" alt="Baixar Clipes Twitch Interface DownKingo" class="w-full h-auto object-cover opacity-90 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity" />
                 </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section id="faq" class="py-24 px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto border-t border-white/5">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase text-white mb-12 text-center tracking-widest">Dúvidas sobre o Twitch Downloader</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
            <details class="group bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 rounded-none open:bg-white/[0.04] transition-colors">
                <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer list-none font-bold text-white text-sm uppercase tracking-wide">
                    Como baixar VODs da Twitch?
                    <Icon name="lucide:chevron-down" class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform text-white/50" width={16} />
                </summary>
                <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-muted font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed border-t border-white/5 pt-4">
                    Copie o link do VOD ou clipe da Twitch, cole no DownKingo e clique em baixar. O aplicativo detectará o conteúdo automaticamente e oferecerá opções de qualidade para download em MP4.
                </div>
            </details>

            <details class="group bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 rounded-none open:bg-white/[0.04] transition-colors">
                 <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer list-none font-bold text-white text-sm uppercase tracking-wide">
                    Posso baixar streams ao vivo?
                    <Icon name="lucide:chevron-down" class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform text-white/50" width={16} />
                </summary>
                <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-muted font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed border-t border-white/5 pt-4">
                    O DownKingo permite gravar streams ao vivo da Twitch em tempo real. Basta colar o link do canal durante a transmissão e o aplicativo gravará o conteúdo até que você decida parar.
                </div>
            </details>

             <details class="group bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 rounded-none open:bg-white/[0.04] transition-colors">
                 <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer list-none font-bold text-white text-sm uppercase tracking-wide">
                    Os VODs deletados podem ser recuperados?
                    <Icon name="lucide:chevron-down" class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform text-white/50" width={16} />
                </summary>
                <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-muted font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed border-t border-white/5 pt-4">
                    Infelizmente, após a exclusão de um VOD pela Twitch, não é possível recuperá-lo. Recomendamos baixar seus VODs favoritos assim que estiverem disponíveis, antes que o streamer ou a Twitch os removam.
                </div>
            </details>
        </div>
    </section>

</BaseLayout>
